readable.content: A man in a red shirt is jumping from one rock to another larger rocker with two male spotters below him . A man is hanging from the edge of a rock while two others catch him . a man jumping from one large rock to the next A man jumps from one boulder to another and two men try to catch him as he barely makes it .
